Episode 19 is an episode in the Yo-Kai Watch anime series.

Summary[]

Komasan helps Dandai's president get in touch with his daughter, again, because she is looking for a new dance craze. Keita discovers that his classmates are possessed by the Yo-Kai Baku who is only looking for a particularly tasty dream to eat. Kyuubi attempts to steal Fumi's heart at the amusement park, but is not prepared for the human world's thrill rides.
